<p>

<font color=white>---</font><a href=http://people.math.gatech.edu/~dmargalit7/papers/dil.pdf> The lower central series and pseudo-Anosov dilatations</a>, Benson Farb, Chris Leininger, and Dan Margalit

<p>

<font color=white>---</font><a href=http://people.math.gatech.edu/~dmargalit7/papers/normal.pdf>Normal generators for mapping class groups are abundant</a>, Justin Lanier and Dan Margalit

<p>

<font color=white>---</font><a href=https://www3.nd.edu/~andyp/papers/GenJohnson2.pdf>On finite generation of the Johnson filtrations</a>, Thomas Church, Mikhail Ershov, Andy Putman

